text: Ðis is þære healfan hide landgemæro æt mæwi.
Ærest on cleaca þonne adun on mæwi of ælbroc.
Þonne on ælbroc of þone æwylman.
Þonne east on gerihte to þam merc stane.
Of þam merc stane to þam blacan pytte & þanne on gerihte to odda wylle.
Adun on odda wylles lace to þan ford lace.
Upp on stream to þam æwylman, þanon eastrihte to boc sætena hig wege.
Þonne ut on þone hig weg to þam cyric wege, þanon on gerihte to þam mere.
Of þam mere to edswyþe torre.
Fram edswyðe torre on gerihte eft on cleaca.
Þis is þære <healfan> <hide> landboc to mæwi þe cnut cing het gebocian æþerice his þegene on ece yrfe.
